OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FSheffield United bosses knew
OL,8,Fmidfielder Maddy Cusack had issues
OL,9,Fwith her former coach before they
OL,10,Fhired him to manage the women's team,
OL,11,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,13,FMaddy Cusack, 27, was found
OL,14,Funresponsive at her home in Horsley in
OL,15,FDerbyshire on 20th September 2023
OL,16,Fafter her coach, Jonathan Morgan made
OL,17,Fcomments about her weight and
OL,18,Frelationship.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe inquest into her death began on
OL,8,Fthe 29th of June and is set to last
OL,9,Ffor two weeks.
OL,11,FThe inquest heard that the player's
OL,12,Ffamily sent a written complaint to
OL,13,FUnited within a week of her death,
OL,14,Foutlining issues they alleged stemmed
OL,15,Ffrom her time working under Mr Morgan.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe club's head of football
OL,8,Fadministration, Carl Shieber told the
OL,9,Finquest on Wednesday that Mr Morgan
OL,10,Fwas 'transparent' about his
OL,11,Frelationship with Miss Cusack, who he
OL,12,Fworked with years earlier at Leicester
OL,13,FCity, during an informal chat before
OL,14,Fhe was recruited by United in February
OL,15,F2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that Mr Morgan
OL,8,Facknowledged that he and Miss Cusack
OL,9,Fhad difficulties at Leicester which he
OL,10,Fsaid had resolved and 'was capable of
OL,11,Fworking in a professional manner with
OL,12,Fher.'
OL,14,FMaddy Cusack joined Birmingham City in
OL,15,F2017 and spent a year there before
OL,16,Fmoving to Leicester City in 2018.
OL,18,FShe then joined Sheffield United in
OL,19,FJanuary 2019.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMaria Mulla, representing Miss
OL,8,FCusack's family, asked Mr Shieber:
OL,9,F"It's correct, isn't it, that in your
OL,10,Fstatement you said Mr Morgan told you
OL,11,Fthere have been some difficulties
OL,12,Fbetween him and Maddy at Leicester?"
OL,14,FMr Shieber told the inquest: "In his
OL,15,Finterview, Maddy was mentioned along
OL,16,Fwith a couple of other players. He
OL,17,Fspoke fondly about Maddy and light-
OL,18,Fheartedly about (how) there had been
OL,19,Fsome moments or issues.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@dO]vD@^OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"I felt Mr Morgan was being very
OL,8,Ftransparent in his relationship with
OL,9,Fher."
OL,11,FHe added: "It's not uncommon for
OL,12,Fplayers and managers to have a
OL,13,Fdifference of opinion regarding
OL,14,Fselection.
OL,16,F"Mr Morgan said ... their paths had
OL,17,Fcrossed and were on a good working
OL,18,Frelationship. They even laughed and
OL,19,Fjoked about the time they had at
OL,20,FLeicester."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@EO]sD@KOUxD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAsked if he told Miss Cusack the club
OL,8,Fwas considering hiring Mr Morgan, Mr
OL,9,FShieber said: "In any industry, you
OL,10,Fwould not be approaching the junior
OL,11,Femployees about the appointment of a
OL,12,Fmanager."
OL,14,FThe inquest previously heard that Mr
OL,15,FMorgan called Miss Cusack "bottom
OL,16,Fheavy" which he said was referencing
OL,17,Fher muscular legs and said "here come
OL,18,Fthe girlfriends" when Miss Cusack was
OL,19,Fwalking with her partner and United
OL,20,Fteammate Grace Riglar.
OL,26,@qD@OOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe previously denied calling Miss
OL,8,FCusack a "psycho" from the sidelines
OL,9,Fduring a match before he joined United.
OL,11,FMr Shieber said that Mr Morgan was
OL,12,Fincluded in a shortlist of recommended
OL,13,Fcandidates to take over as United
OL,14,Fwomen's coach.
OL,16,FThe inquest heard that the club's
OL,17,Fformer women's team manager said that
OL,18,FMr Morgan "doesn't have the greatest
OL,19,Freputation in the game but he has a
OL,20,Fgood CV."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783687767
OL,3,CSheffield United knew Maddy Cusack had
OL,4,C'difficulties' with coach, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FWhen Mr Shieber asked Ms Johnson to
OL,8,Fclarify what she meant, she said he
OL,9,Fhad been "a bit of a dick", the
OL,10,Finquest heard.
OL,12,FMr Shieber told the inquest: "I spoke
OL,13,Fto Zoe Johnson about this. I don't
OL,14,Fremember exactly what she said. She
OL,15,Fsaid he had been a bit of a dick."
OL,17,FMr Shieber said the description was
OL,18,Frelated to a "single incident".
OL,20,FThe inquest continues.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@ZO]tD@^OUwD@bO]zD@NOUzD@^O]
